00:03:37.320 --> 00:03:37.680
Let's go!

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:42.800
Hurry, hurry!

00:03:43.320 --> 00:03:44.040
Faster!

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:47.120
Make way!

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:52.080
