00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:22.920
Doesn't it look like you?

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:26.640
Can't you say something nice

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.760
to cheer me up?

00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:37.960
Thank you, wicked fox.

00:04:41.200 --> 00:04:42.200
It's getting late.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:42.960
Princess,

00:04:43.320 --> 00:04:44.400
you should return to the palace.

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:47.320
Princess,

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:49.520
we should head back.

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.360
Let's go.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.960
Can I still visit you at Rui Residence?

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.680
As long as it's not to see Third Brother,

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.560
I always welcome your visit, Princess.

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:12.800
Got it.

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:27.600
Thank you, Second Young Master Rui.

00:05:27.640 --> 00:05:29.200
