00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:00.600
they deliberately made the Prince

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.040
eat undercooked mushrooms.

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:04.360
Doesn't that mean this banquet...

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:05.800
Of course not.

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:07.680
Father and General Qiao

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.200
and my colleagues at the Hanlin Academy

00:06:09.200 --> 00:06:10.400
all get along very well.

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:12.080
And a few other officials

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:12.840
