00:06:57.200 --> 00:06:58.280
Lately,

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:00.560
I've been heartbroken by scholars.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:03.640
I just want to see the wide world.

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:05.520
It'd be best to meet

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:08.280
a brave man like General of the Cloud Banner.

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:10.280
