00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:24.000
I want to leave the palace and see the real world.

00:07:25.880 --> 00:07:28.640
Wang Guanshan just released a new storybook.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.640
Should I get it for Princess to read?

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:32.080
What storybook?

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:36.280
Didn't I say before,

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.080
