Another wants Yan Luo to wed Qian Yuan's second prince.

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:22.000
Is Qian Yuan really that threatening to me?

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:22.880
Left Minister.

00:08:23.080 --> 00:08:24.200
It's also for Ling An.

00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:25.080
Left Minister.

00:08:25.080 --> 00:08:25.760
Your Majesty.

00:08:25.760 --> 00:08:26.880
